columns.name: ssh_public_key_id
columns.description: The ID for this ssh public key key.

columns.name: user_name
columns.description: The name of the IAM user that the key is associated with.

columns.name: status
columns.description: The status of the ssh public key. Active means that the key is valid for API calls; Inactive means it is not.

columns.name: update_date
columns.description: The date when the ssh public key was last updated.
